// Font size variables
//
// A scale of sizes has been defined for its use along the different elements of the theme.
// As it happens with many other sizing scales variables go from XS to XXXL
// Every size is relative to a base font size that may be modified. In that case all the other sizes will change in relationship to this new base size.
// With the exception of this base font size expressed in pixels, font sizes are expressed in rem units.
//
// $sc-font-size-xxs - Double extra small font size
// $sc-font-size-xs - Extra small font size
// $sc-font-size-s - Small font size
// $sc-font-size-m - Medium font size
// $sc-font-size-l - Large font size
// $sc-font-size-xl - Extra large font size
// $sc-font-size-xxl - Double extra large font size
// $sc-font-size-xxxl - Triple extra large font size
